33 (E) Garlic-in-oil mixtures that are not modified in a way that
34 results in mixtures that do not support the growth or formation
35 described in subsection (a).
36 (3) Except as specified in subsection (c)(4) and (c)(5), a food that
37 involves an interaction of pH and Aw for control of spores in food
38 that is heat treated to destroy vegetative cells and subsequently
39 packaged that results in:
40 (A) an Aw value greater than 0.92 but less than or equal to
41 0.95 and a pH value greater than 5.6; or
42 (B) an Aw value greater than 0.95 and a pH value greater than
